## Customizing Shadcn/ui Components

### Theme Configuration
Edit `tailwind.config.mjs` to customize colors, fonts, and other design tokens.

### Component Customization
Shadcn/ui components are copied to your project, so you can modify them directly in `src/components/ui/`.

### Adding Custom Variants
```tsx
// In component file
const buttonVariants = cva(
  "inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md",
  {
    variants: {
      variant: {
        default: "bg-primary text-primary-foreground",
        custom: "bg-purple-600 text-white", // Your custom variant
      },
    },
  }
);
```

